          <p>
            The public cloud market was valued at $500 billion in 2022 and
            30% of it has been wasted on unused or underutilized resources.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="text-center mb-3">
            <svg class="text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-rocket"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"/><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"/><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"/><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"/></svg>
          </div>


          <p>
            Managing cloud spend has become a top challenge for all organizations.
            We are building a solution to help you stop cloud waste.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="text-secondary text-center mt-5"><strong>CloudWaste</strong> is made by <a href="https://vinua.com">Vinua</a></p>
</div>
